      • getPropertyById

        public <T> PropertyData<T> getPropertyById(String id)
        Description copied from interface: QueryResult
        Returns a property by ID.

        Because repositories are not obligated to add property IDs to their query result properties, this method might not always work as expected with some repositories. Use QueryResult.getPropertyByQueryName(String) instead.

        Specified by:
